David L. Craddock is one of the major voices in long-form videogame journalism, having written books about Diablo, Shovel Knight, and Pillars of Eternity, among others.
“I really, really respected him for that,” Craddock says, “because he wanted me to do my journalist thing.
It was just a magical time.”Listen to the complete interview with David L. Craddock in Episode 397 of Geek’s Guide to the Galaxy (above).
